== Truncate

Provides a way to truncate content. Documentation and examples are provided in the description
of the <r:truncate /> tag.

== Authors and Credits
 
Written by Anton Astashov, with Brenton Cheng, for Astrology.com (a division of iVillage Inc.)
Refactored and enhanced by Jim Gay of Saturn Flyer with code from Benjamin Thomas (http://benjaminthomas.org/2009/01/30/smart-html-truncate.html)